<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Nitak kanima fehna ho ƲIT112</title>
<time_sig>C.M. (8.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<aka>Meditation on Death</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Nitak kanima fehna ho̱
 Si ai illi hokma,
 A̱ki ʋba binili mʋt
 Is sa halanlashke.

[V2]
 Chisʋs pulla tuk mak ona,
 Si ai illi hokmʋt,
 Ʋba yakni achukma ka
 Ona la hi oke.

[V3]
 Chihowa pulla kak ocha
 A̱ nukha̱klo hokma,
 Ʋba yakni pilla hoka
 Ona la hi oke.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>112</hymn_number>
</song>